PrecisRe-appointment of Thomas H.B. Symons, of Peterborough, Ontario, as a member of the Historic Sites and Monuments Board of Canada, as a representative of the Province of Ontario to hold office during pleasure for a period of five years; and designation of the said Thomas H.B. Symons as Chairman of the Historic Sites and Monuments Board of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a period of five years, effective June 2, 1991.
